      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, having been curated with exacting standards and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The bodywork is flawless, retaining its original factory depth, while the interior is devoid of any discernible wear. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and reliability of a new delivery. This represents a rare acquisition for the collector who prioritizes uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
