    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely obsessed with this car, but life changes mean it's time for her to find a new garage. Seriously, this beauty is in breathtaking condition\u2014it's been pampered, garage-kept, and honestly looks like it just came off the showroom floor! It's spotless inside and out, drives like an absolute dream, and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by and see just how stunning it is in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
