    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality specimen that looks, feels, and smells as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been fastidiously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and UV exposure. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections; a professional-grade ceramic coating has been applied to ensure the finish remains breathtaking. The factory alloy wheels are absolutely pristine, showing no curb rash or oxidation, and are paired with high-performance tires with near-full tread depth. Moving inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear or creasing, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-wallet philosophy, documented by a comprehensive binder of service records. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, showing no leaks, corrosion, or grime. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
