      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered and kept in a garage, so it\u2019s looking flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come swing by and see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
